{"tid":2364910,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"高牆內的香港人 - 高慧然","createTime":"2021-01-13T10:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T10:42:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d993952de437135bd36904c88691e482e9676388","tid":2364910,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T10:42:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210113/E54LIMFJQBH2RITP2MKKWQMFS4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210113%2FE54LIMFJQBH2RITP2MKKWQMFS4%2F&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEZq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=968a7355\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210113%2FE54LIMFJQBH2RITP2MKKWQMFS4%2F&h=947509b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210113/E54LIMFJQBH2RITP2MKKWQMFS4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n高牆內的香港人 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/p4Wdy-oeazQWTa-msuz3g1XU1vs=/1981x1613/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LFF2ZSDZBBGTLAF27M2WICSXFE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp4Wdy-oeazQWTa-msuz3g1XU1vs%3D%2F1981x1613%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLFF2ZSDZBBGTLAF27M2WICSXFE.jpg&h=d64e3697&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n近日寒流襲港，香港朋友紛紛提及濕凍的痛苦。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。一離開被窩，馬上被寒氣裹住，連去一趟廁所都是好大的掙扎。<br />\n<br />\n有朋友說最大的掙扎是沖涼。因為浴室沒有插電孔，所以無法放置防水暖風機。在透風的浴室中除衫除褲，會全身打冷顫。還有人家中使用舊式的儲水式熱水器，煲熱一機水，就要速戰速決在幾分鐘內沖完涼洗完頭。到下一位沖涼時又要重新煲水。<br />\n<br />\n這麼冷的天氣，想想高牆內的香港人，很難受。外面再寒冷，總有辦法解決問題，出錢請師傅安裝插電孔，或使用拖板。換一個熱水器，在浴室安裝浴室寶。多穿幾件衣服，攬住個熱水袋都是解決問題的方法。<br />\n<br />\n可是寒流下，高牆內的香港人，只能死頂死捱，單薄的囚衣和被鋪，冷硬的囚牀&hellip;&hellip;在獄中再度被捕的黃之鋒，被押解往石壁監獄時，沒有冷衫，沒有羽絨，想必很冷。最令人擔憂的是72歲高齡的肥佬黎，他意志堅強，但生理上，畢竟是個老人。他們做錯了甚麼，要受到這樣的折磨？<br />\n<br />\nFacebook：kowaiyin.yoyoko"}]}